gntheorie und -didaktik wird hier exemplarisch entfaltet.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aMüll. 4aMüllmanagement. 4aMüllvermeidung. 4aProduktdesign. 7aDESIGN / Product.2bisacsh  a- waste - product design - waste management.1 aErlhoff, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2018z9783110602999oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG0 cEPUBz97830356176270 cprintz978303561679840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303561760340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035617603423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035617603/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017